title: (PSX-PSP) Syphon Filter 3 converted properly (Kingdom-games by K
description:
SYPHON FILTER 3:

The enthralling Syphon Filter story takes another twist as heroes Gabe Logan and Lian Xing find themselves framed -- accused of attempting to spread the mysterious synthetic weapon they had fought so hard to destroy. Playing as both Logan and Xing, set off on an action-packed voyage of discovery as the two fugitives attempt to blow the conspiracy wide open and reveal the sinister origins of the deadly Syphon Filter project...


Tested and working on all CFW's 5.00 m33 and above using the 500 popsloader pack set on 3.72 POPS...KloWn
